dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Depths shown by soundings. Map shows international boundaries and administrative divisions, oil pipelines and fields, ruins, ferry lines. Includes indexed lists of "Counties of Romania with their capitals," "Counties of Hungary with their capitals," and "Administrative divisions of Bosnia and Herzegovina" and notes.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : National Geographic Society, c2010.
dct_subject_sm: Bosnia and Herzegovina—Administrative and political divisions—Maps
dcat_theme_sm: Bosnia and Herzegovina—Administrative and political divisions—Maps
